nt%20to%20bite%20my%20cyanide%20capsule.%20If%20I%20ever%20start%20using%20Siri%20out%20loud%20at%20my%20desk%20in%20the%20office%2C%20I%20fully%20accept%20that%20HR%20can%20fire%20me%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Of%20course%2C%20voice-controlled%20devices%20are%20an%20accessibility%20issue%20for%20some%20people%20who%20are%20blind%2C%20have%20low%20vision%2C%20or%20otherwise%20have%20trouble%20using%20a%20screen%20device.%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20this%20use%2C%20which%20is%20obviously%20good%20and%20a%20benefit.%20Perhaps%20society%20would%20be%20better%20if%20public%20use%20of%20voice%20devices%20were%20more%20normalized!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-openai-company-chatgpt-elon-musk-founded-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20voice.%20At%20a%20demonstration%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20it%20showed%20new%20voices%20that%20could%20talk%20to%20you%20(this%20was%20the%20demonstration%20that%20infamously%20got%20them%20in%20trouble%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-scarlett-johansson-saga-reveals-a-deeper-problem-with-ai-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScarlett%20Johansson%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20making%20a%20voice%20option%20suspiciously%20close%20to%20her%20own).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20also%20embraced%20the%20idea%20of%20voice%20controls.%20Its%20stand-alone%20Meta%20AI%20app%20is%20meant%20for%20natural%20conversations%20between%20you%20and%20the%20app%20on%20your%20phone%20(though%2C%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20it's%20laggy%20and%20often%20leads%20to%20crosstalk).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20long-held%20sci-fi%20dream%20to%20have%20a%20supersmart%20AI%20agent%20you%20can%20just%20talk%20to%20naturally.%20Like%20Tony%20Stark's%20Jarvis%2C%20or%20the%20ScarJo%20voice%20in%20%26quot%3BHer.%26quot%3B%20But%20even%20%26quot%3BKnight%20Rider%26quot%3B%20had%20the%20basic%20understanding%2