Kantrowitz%20during%20a%20live%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-google-co-founder%2Fid1522960417%3Fi%3D1000709250044%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20onstage%20at%20Google's%20IO%20developer%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20anybody%20who's%20a%20computer%20scientist%20should%20not%20be%20retired%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Brin%20said%20alongside%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepMind%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Alphabet%2C%20is%20the%20research%20lab%20behind%20the%20company's%20AI%20projects%2C%20including%20its%20genAI%20assistant%20Gemini.%20Brin%20told%20Kantrowitz%20that%20he's%20at%20Google%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20much%20every%20day%20now%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20with%20training%20the%20latest%20models%20from%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20artificial%20intelligence%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20competitive%20and%20near-constantly%20changing%20tech%20field%2C%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unique%20time%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Brin.%20When%20Kantrowitz%20asked%20if%20his%20return%20was%20solely%20about%20competing%20with%20rivals%20who%20are%20working%20toward%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Esystems%2C%20Brin%20said%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20the%20AI%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20never%20been%20a%20greater%2C%20sort%20of%2C%20problem%20and%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20greater%20cusp%20of%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20additional%20comments%20from%20Brin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20witnessed