04901817bc45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank.%3Cp%3ESpc.%20Christian%20Carrillo%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENearly%2030%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tanks%20will%20roll%20down%20Constitution%20Ave.%20in%20DC%20for%20the%20Army's%20250th%20birthday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20service%20is%20finalizing%20plans%20to%20prevent%20the%20heavy%2070-ton%20tanks%20from%20damaging%20the%20road.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEngineers%20will%20use%20steel%20plates%20and%20track%20pads%20to%20protect%20roads%20during%20the%20parade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20powerful%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank%2C%20with%20its%20heavy%20armor%20and%20120mm%20cannon%2C%20is%20a%20massive%20hulk%20of%20steel%2C%20and%20dozens%20are%20set%20to%20hit%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20nation's%20capital%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2030%20of%20the%20tanks%20are%20expected%20to%20rumble%20down%20Constitution%20Avenue%20as%20part%20of%20the%20US%20Army's%20250th%20anniversary%20celebration%20on%20June%2014%2C%20set%20to%20coincide%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20street%2C%20which%20runs%20parallel%20to%20the%20National%20Mall%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20major%20route%20for%20city%20traffic%2C%20isn't%20built%20to%20easily%20accommodate%20each%20tank's%20nearly%2070-ton%20frame.%20Most%20cars%20weigh%20only%20about%20two%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20is%20the%20Army%20going%20to%20keep%20its%20tanks%20from%20chewing%20up%20Constitution%20Avenue%3F%20The%20service's%20engineers%20are%20putting%20the%20finishing%20touches%20on%20plans%20to%20protect%20the%20busy%20street's%20pavement%20from%20biting%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20aren't%20too%20concerned%20with%20the%20straight%20path%20down%20Constitution%2C%20which%20will%20likely%20see%20a%20single%20file%20of%20tanks.%20It's%20turning%20points%20that%20will%20be%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20tears%20from%20the%20heavy%20tracked%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20targeting%20those%20areas%20that%20we%20have%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Army%20Col.%20Jesse%20Curry%2C%20Executive%20Officer%20for%20the%20Army's%20Chief%20of%20Engineers%2C%20during%20a%20media%20roundtable%20with%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BParticularly%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20pavement%20would%20typically%2C%20you%20know%2C%20receive%20an%20exaggerated%20level%20of%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tanks%20arrive%20via%20rail%20at%20Grafenwoehr%2C%20Germany%2C%20May%2012%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f602cc6ad288d1481acdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tanks%20arrive%20via%20rail%20at%20Grafenwoehr%2C%20Germany.%3Cp%3EStaff%20Sgt.%20Christopher%20Stewart%2FU.S.%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20such%20stress%2C%20military%20engineers%20are%20figuring%20out%20which%20turn%20points%20will%20be%20layered%20with%20steel%20plates%20at%20least%20one%20inch%20thick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20large%20plates%20are%20commonly%20seen%20on%20city%20streets%20where%20heavy%20equipment%20is%20used%2C%20Curry%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20equipment%20staging%20areas%20and%20the%20parade%20route%20were%20specially%20chosen%20to%20minimize%20weight-related%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeavy%20tracked%20vehicles%20like%20the%20M1A1%20often%20make%20turns%20by%20using%20differential%20steering%20%E2%80%94%20one%20side%20will%20roll%20forward%20while%20the%20other%20reverses%2C%20or%20the%20tracks%20will%20operate%20at%20a%20different%20speed.%20That%20can%20cause%20tracks%20to%20%26quot%3Bpinch%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20problem%20for%20asphalt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInbound%20parade%20tanks%20will%20also%20don%20new%20%26quot%3Btrack%20pads%2C%26quot%3B%20rubber%20components%20that%20create%20some%20separation%20between%20the%20metal%20tracks%20and%20the%20pavement%2C%20Curry%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditional%20measures%20to%20prevent%20damage%20are%20still%20being%20examined%2C%20with%20help%20from%20DC's%20Department%20of%20Transportation%2C%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20(which%20oversees%20maintenance%20of%20the%20National%20Mall)%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Highway%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tanks%20and%20other%20vehicles%2C%20such%20as%20Bradley%20fighting%20vehicles%20and%20Strykers%2C%20will%20arrive%20in%20the%20DC%20area%20via%20rail%20and%20will%20then%20depart%20to%20parade%20staging%20areas%20via%20heavy-duty%20trailers%2C%20similar%20to%20those%20used%20to%20move%20houses%20down%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226198%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20M1A1%20SEP%20V3%20Abrams%20is%20loaded%20on%20to%20a%20heavy%20equipment%20movement%20truck%20on%20Fort%20Cavazos%2C%20Texas%2C%20March%204%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f60bcca50259add4cce71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224132%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20M1A1%20Abrams%20is%20loaded%20onto%20a%20heavy%20equipment%20movement%20truck%20at%20Fort%20Cavazos%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ESpc.%20Alejandro%20L.%20Carrasquel%2F%20US%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETroops%20will%20not%20be%20conducting%20any%20full-scale%20rehearsals%20for%20the%20parade%2C%20a%20notable%20deviation%20from%20typical%20military%20planning.%20Normally%2C%20complete%20rehearsals%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20any%20military%20mission%2C%20including%20small%20unit%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20while%20the%20Army%20has%20been%20planning%20a%20major%20250th%20birthday%20event%20for%20two%20years%2C%20the%20idea%20to%20include%20heavy%20vehicles%20like%20tanks%20and%20other%20armored%20vehicles%20in%20a%20parade%20only%20arrived%20t