%20children.%20Under%20the%20plan%2C%20babies%20born%20after%20January%2031%2C%202024%20and%20before%20January%201%2C%202029%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%2C%20the%20last%20three%20years%20of%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20term%20%E2%80%94%20will%20receive%20%241%2C000%20for%20the%20account%20from%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20name%20was%20an%20acronym%20for%20%26quot%3BMoney%20Account%20for%20Growth%20and%20Advancement%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20initials%20as%20Trump's%20political%20movement.%20In%20a%20last-minute%20change%20before%20the%20House%20passed%20their%20version%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%26quot%3B%20on%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BMAGA%26quot%3B%20was%20replaced%20with%20%26quot%3BTrump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20president%20stands%20to%20get%20the%20credit%2C%20it%20was%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz's%20idea%20to%20create%20%26quot%3BInvest%20America%26quot%3B%20accounts.%20The%20Texas%20Republican%20says%20he%20doesn't%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20care%20is%20that%20they%20remain%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20provision's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20larger%20bill.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20they're%20called.%20What%20it%20matters%20is%20what%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20political%20branding%2C%20it's%20further%20than%20other%20recent%20presidents%20have%20gone.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20chose%20not%20to%20sign%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-stimulus-checks-rescue-plan-covid-relief-bill-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20stimulus%20checks%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Trump%20did%20%E2%80%94%20though%20he%20later%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bstupid%26quot%3B%20not%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOt