C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20conversation%20that%20really%20stayed%20with%20me%20was%20a%20quick%20interaction%20with%20Hon.%20Shri%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry.%20As%20we%20spoke%2C%20he%20said%20something%20that%20struck%20a%20chord%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20full%20of%20opportunities%20for%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%20That%20line%20perfectly%20captured%20the%20energy%20in%20the%20room.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20trade%E2%80%94it%20was%20about%20creating%20an%20economic%20corridor%20that%20connects%20continents%20through%20shared%20values%3A%20climate%20resilience%2C%20digital%20innovation%2C%20and%20inclusive%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%20with%20Hon.%20Shri%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industry%2C%20at%20the%20India-Mediterranean%20Business%20Conclave%202024%2C%20discussing%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20building%20sustainable%2C%20strategic%20economic%20corridors.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192519.382_11zon-1747749352-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co