ience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%E2%80%99s%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%202024%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20high-level%20delegations%20from%20member%20countries%2C%20discussing%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20regional%20collaboration%20in%20addressing%20shared%20challenges.%20Climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20adaptation%2C%20and%20environmental%20sustainability%20are%20now%20fundamental%20pillars%20within%20BIMSTEC%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20framework%2C%20reflecting%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20cooperative%20solutions%20across%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%2C%20comprising%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20India%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20Thailand%20%E2%80%93%20is%20emerging%20as%20a%20key%20platform%20for%20regional%20economic%20integration%20with%20sustainability%20at%20its%20core.%20At%20the%202024%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20engagement%20took%20center%20stage%20as%20member%20nations%20underscored%20their%20collective%20commitment%20to%20climate%20resilience%2C%20clean%20technology%20collaboration%2C%20and%20inclusive%20development%20across%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20green%20trade%20facilitation%20and%20eco-tourism%20infrastructure%20to%20nanotech%20for%20clean%20water%20and%20climate%20policy%20coordination%2C%20BIMSTEC%20is%20aligning%20economic%20integration%20with%20environmental%20stewardship.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions%2C%20this%20collaboration%20offers%20a%20powerful%20model%20for%20shared%20resilience%2C%20knowledge%20exchange%2C%20and%20inclusive%2C%20low-carbon%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20region%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20impacts%20such%20as%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20extr